The documentation in onnx.proto is somewhat misleading because the comment above GraphProto.initializer implies inputs to the graph can be initialized with default values:

> // A list of named tensor values (constants), used to specify default
  // values for some of the inputs of the graph...
  repeated TensorProto initializer = 5;
